Robert W. Lazar's Biography




			Career and Education Highlights:      .Senior Advisor to TBC Accounting Firm (2011 to present)  .President and CEO of the New York Business Development Corporation (1988 to 2005), Director Emeritus (2005 to present)  .Chairman of the University of Albany School of Business Advisory Board (2006 to present)  .Consultant to the Independent Bankers Association (2009 to 2011)  .Serves as a Board member for several charitable organizations  .Member, KPMG Audit Committee Institute  .Certified Public Accountant (active member)  .M.S., Accounting, University at Albany  .B.S., Economics, The Sage Colleges
		
Source: Sterling Bancorp on 04/13/2017
		
	

 






