Executive Profile
Robert W. Lazar  Independent Director and Director of Sterling National Bank, Sterling BancorpAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships73$91,733
Background

		Mr. Robert W. Lazar serves as the President and Chief Executive Officer of New York Business Development Corporation. Mr. Lazar has been Senior Advisor of Independent Bankers Association of New York State since 2006. He has an extensive experience, proven track record and reputation in banking and financial services. Mr. Lazar has more than 30 years of diverse financial services experience, particularly with regard to promoting the expansion and growth of businesses ... in New York before joining Sterling Bancorp's Board. He served as President and Chief Executive Officer of Empire State Certified Development Corporation from 1987 to 2005. He also served as President and Chief Executive Officer of Statewide Zone Capital Corporation from 1999 to 2005. He served as Senior Advisor of New York Business Development Corporation from 1987 to 2005. He serves on the Board of Directors of the St. Peter's Hospital Foundation and University at Albany, among other not-for- profit organizations. He serves on several committees of the New York Bankers Association. He has been Independent Director of Sterling Bancorp since September 8, 2005. He served as a Director of Sterling National Bank since September 8, 2005. He has received numerous awards, such as Small Business Executive of the Year Award from the Capital District Business Review, Small Business Advocate of the Year from Empire State Development Corporation and Entrepreneur of the Year presented by the University at Albany, in addition to awards from schools and community groups for his various achievements. He serves as a Member of Dean's Advisory Board and Member of School of Business Advisory Council at School of Business at the University at Albany. Mr. Lazar is a Certified Public Accountant and holds his BS in Economics from The Sage Colleges and a MS in Accounting from the University of Albany.Read Full Background




